ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 234, \"to\": 246}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday\", \"from\": 250, \"to\": 256}, {\"ngram\": \"18 players\", \"from\": 284, \"to\": 294}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 298, \"to\": 302}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The former Arsenal and Barcelona striker admits he's faced multiple problems with his squad selection as several Premier League clubs have refused to release their players for the tournament.\", \"from\": 307, \"to\": 498, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 318, \"end\": 325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arsenal_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.385436077178222e-24, \"text\": \"Arsenal\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arsenal_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arsenal_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 330, \"end\": 339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Barcelona\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5549463726732918e-25, \"text\": \"Barcelona\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Barcelona\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Barcelona\"}, {\"begin\": 420, \"end\": 434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2156274032692757e-24, \"text\": \"Premier League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"multiple problems\", \"from\": 366, \"to\": 383}, {\"ngram\": \"his squad selection\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 408}, {\"ngram\": \"their players\", \"from\": 465, \"to\": 478}, {\"ngram\": \"the tournament\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 497}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But because the football event at the Olympics is not formally recognised by FIFA, clubs are not obliged to release their players for the competition this summer.\", \"from\": 500, \"to\": 662, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 577, \"end\": 581, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"score\": 0.9999999686056076, \"rank\": 3.139425617913845e-08, \"text\": \"FIFA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the football event\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 530}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 546}, {\"ngram\": \"clubs\", \"from\": 583, \"to\": 588}, {\"ngram\": \"their players\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 629}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 634, \"to\": 649}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Henry's squad will get together in Clairefontaine on June 16, while France will kick off their Olympics group stage against the United States on July 24, before playing Guinea on July 27 and New Zealand on July 30.\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 878, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 732, \"end\": 738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.281621614123354e-29, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 792, \"end\": 805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.99999982162082, \"rank\": 1.7787474051120628e-07, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 855, \"end\": 866, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9995217841814851, \"rank\": 0.0003497764099553549, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Henry's squad\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 677}, {\"ngram\": \"Clairefontaine\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 713}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 721}, {\"ngram\": \"their Olympics group stage\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 779}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 813}, {\"ngram\": \"Guinea\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 839}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 847}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 874}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'You have to know that it's not easy to find yourself in a situation where you have to go and ask a certain club for permission to be able to take their players when you actually can not ask for anything since they are within their right not to send since it's not a FIFA date.\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 1157, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1147, \"end\": 1151, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"score\": 0.9999999686056076, \"rank\": 3.139425617913845e-08, \"text\": \"FIFA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a situation\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 948}, {\"ngram\": \"a certain club\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 992}, {\"ngram\": \"permission\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1007}, {\"ngram\": \"their players\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1040}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1083}, {\"ngram\": \"their right\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1117}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When it's already a FIFA date it's hard, so there you go, we are trying to find ways to have certain players and believe me it's not easy,' Henry said after unveiling his provisional squad.\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1347, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1178, \"end\": 1182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"score\": 0.9999999686056076, \"rank\": 3.13942561