unich\", \"from\": 2976, \"to\": 2989}, {\"ngram\": \"Ugochukwu\", \"from\": 3028, \"to\": 3037}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was told, 'no'.\", \"from\": 3083, \"to\": 3100, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I do not know if you have ever been to speak to someone when you know that you can not argue.\", \"from\": 3102, \"to\": 3196, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 3151, \"to\": 3158}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'You are asking me questions but Chelsea are not me, so I asked questions about players, I was told, 'no, it's not possible, you can have Ugochukwu', I know it's not me who said that, that's what happened, I can not direct you on the why and how and I understand a little more the level of difficulty if a player ends up at the Euros because doing both is not easy.'\", \"from\": 3198, \"to\": 3564, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3231, \"end\": 3238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.209695279007921e-28, \"text\": \"Chelsea\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"questions\", \"from\": 3217, \"to\": 3226}, {\"ngram\": \"questions\", \"from\": 3262, \"to\": 3271}, {\"ngram\": \"players\", \"from\": 3278, \"to\": 3285}, {\"ngram\": \"Ugochukwu\", \"from\": 3336, \"to\": 3345}, {\"ngram\": \"the level\", \"from\": 3475, \"to\": 3484}, {\"ngram\": \"difficulty\", \"from\": 3488, \"to\": 3498}, {\"ngram\": \"a player\", \"from\": 3502, \"to\": 3510}, {\"ngram\": \"the Euros\", \"from\": 3522, \"to\": 3531}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked if he is disappointed by the decisions made by Premier League clubs, Henry replied: 'I will respond to this one very, very clearly - it's not the time for me to talk about that, firstly.\", \"from\": 3566, \"to\": 3758, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the decisions\", \"from\": 3597, \"to\": 3610}, {\"ngram\": \"Premier League clubs\", \"from\": 3619, \"to\": 3639}, {\"ngram\": \"Henry\", \"from\": 3641, \"to\": 3646}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 3714, \"to\": 3722}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Secondly, am I disappointed or surprised?\", \"from\": 3760, \"to\": 3802, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No.\", \"from\": 3803, \"to\": 3806, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Neither disappointed or surprised, the clubs are within their rights, unfortunately, and I think what I have been saying has not changed since I started taking about the Olympics.\", \"from\": 3807, \"to\": 3986, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the clubs\", \"from\": 3842, \"to\": 3851}, {\"ngram\": \"their rights\", \"from\": 3863, \"to\": 3875}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3973, \"to\": 3985}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We knew very well that we were going to be confronted by this, you are waiting for a response hoping but at a given moment if you give the possibility to a club they are within their rights to say, 'no'.\", \"from\": 3987, \"to\": 4190, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a response\", \"from\": 4070, \"to\": 4080}, {\"ngram\": \"a given moment\", \"from\": 4095, \"to\": 4109}, {\"ngram\": \"the possibility\", \"from\": 4122, \"to\": 4137}, {\"ngram\": \"a club\", \"from\": 4141, \"to\": 4147}, {\"ngram\": \"their rights\", \"from\": 4164, \"to\": 4176}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It becomes difficult, so am I disappointed, surprised?\", \"from\": 4191, \"to\": 4245, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No, I expected it.'\", \"from\": 4246, \"to\": 4265, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Henry also made it clear that there was little chance of including Kylian Mbappe, who is set to complete his move to Real Madrid this week.\", \"from\": 4267, \"to\": 4406, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4334, \"end\": 4347, \"title\": 